title: The Richard Sherman Podcast - Are Bengals, Broncos, Packers, Bucs & Rams done? Or are they still playoff teams?
itunes:title: The Richard Sherman Podcast - Are Bengals, Broncos, Packers, Bucs & Rams done? Or are they still playoff teams?
description:
Richard debuts a new segment called Shermanator where he decides whetether NFL teams still have a shot at the playoffs or if it's hasta la vista, baby. He predicts the future for the Cincinnati Bengals, Denver Broncos, Green Bay Packers, Tampa Bay Buccaneers, and Los Angeles Rams. Richard and Mitch also discuss the emerging debate at running back in Dallas as Tony Pollard continues to flourish in Ezekiel Elliott's absence. #volume #herd #colincowherd

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
